{
  "title": "Services",
  "subtitle": "AI, cloud, media, and IoT service integrations.",
  "content": [
    {
      "type": "ContentText",
      "title": "Overview",
      "body": "<p>Services are not part of the Strvct core \u2014 they are optional integrations provided as a convenient way to quickly connect with important external services. The <code>Services</code> singleton is the root container for all of them. Each service is a standard Strvct node with slots, persistence, and automatic UI \u2014 the same patterns used for domain objects apply to service configuration. Users can inspect and configure services (API keys, model selection, proxy settings) through the generated interface without any custom settings UI.</p>\n<svg viewBox=\"0 0 820 320\" width=\"820\" xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/2000/svg\">\n  <style>\n    text { font-family: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; fill: #111; }\n    .b { font-weight: 600; }\n    .dim { fill: #666; }\n    .box { fill: none; stroke: #111; stroke-width: 1; }\n    .fill { fill: #f0ede5; stroke: #111; stroke-width: 1; }\n    .flow { stroke: #111; stroke-width: 1; fill: none; }\n  </style>\n  <defs>\n    <marker id=\"asv\" viewBox=\"0 0 10 10\" refX=\"9\" refY=\"5\" markerWidth=\"7\" markerHeight=\"7\" orient=\"auto\">\n      <path d=\"M0,0 L10,5 L0,10 z\" fill=\"#111\"/>\n    </marker>\n  </defs>\n  <rect class=\"fill\" x=\"290\" y=\"20\" width=\"240\" height=\"60\"/>\n  <text x=\"410\" y=\"48\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"b\">Services (singleton)</text>\n  <text x=\"410\" y=\"68\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"dim\">root container; standard SvNode tree</text>\n  <line class=\"flow\" x1=\"410\" y1=\"80\" x2=\"410\" y2=\"105\"/>\n  <line class=\"flow\" x1=\"110\" y1=\"105\" x2=\"710\" y2=\"105\"/>\n  <line class=\"flow\" x1=\"110\" y1=\"105\" x2=\"110\" y2=\"135\" marker-end=\"url(#asv)\"/>\n  <line class=\"flow\" x1=\"260\" y1=\"105\" x2=\"260\" y2=\"135\" marker-end=\"url(#asv)\"/>\n  <line class=\"flow\" x1=\"410\" y1=\"105\" x2=\"410\" y2=\"135\" marker-end=\"url(#asv)\"/>\n  <line class=\"flow\" x1=\"560\" y1=\"105\" x2=\"560\" y2=\"135\" marker-end=\"url(#asv)\"/>\n  <line class=\"flow\" x1=\"710\" y1=\"105\" x2=\"710\" y2=\"135\" marker-end=\"url(#asv)\"/>\n  <rect class=\"fill\" x=\"35\" y=\"135\" width=\"150\" height=\"80\"/>\n  <text x=\"110\" y=\"160\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"b\">AI Services</text>\n  <text x=\"110\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"dim\">OpenAI, Anthropic,</text>\n  <text x=\"110\" y=\"198\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"dim\">Gemini, Groq, ...</text>\n  <rect class=\"fill\" x=\"185\" y=\"135\" width=\"150\" height=\"80\"/>\n  <text x=\"260\" y=\"160\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"b\">Cloud Storage</text>\n  <text x=\"260\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"dim\">Firebase, S3</text>\n  <rect class=\"fill\" x=\"335\" y=\"135\" width=\"150\" height=\"80\"/>\n  <text x=\"410\" y=\"160\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"b\">Media</text>\n  <text x=\"410\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"dim\">TTS, image gen,</text>\n  <text x=\"410\" y=\"198\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"dim\">audio playback</text>\n  <rect class=\"fill\" x=\"485\" y=\"135\" width=\"150\" height=\"80\"/>\n  <text x=\"560\" y=\"160\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"b\">Proxies</text>\n  <text x=\"560\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"dim\">CORS bypass,</text>\n  <text x=\"560\" y=\"198\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"dim\">API key handling</text>\n  <rect class=\"fill\" x=\"635\" y=\"135\" width=\"150\" height=\"80\"/>\n  <text x=\"710\" y=\"160\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"b\">Home Assistant</text>\n  <text x=\"710\" y=\"180\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"dim\">IoT integration</text>\n  <text x=\"410\" y=\"280\" text-anchor=\"middle\" class=\"dim\">Each service is an ordinary SvNode subtree; configuration uses the framework's auto-generated UI and persistence.</text>\n</svg>"
    },
